Text:
Thanks again for collection 2.

Just wondering if you have a better copy of "Zero Six Vol 1" from the first manga collection.  It seems to be missing half the book.

Thanks

No, sorry, I don't have a different version of it, and hadn't noticed that there was a problem.  I downloaded the original from www.bakabt.com, which is a private torrent site (have to sign up to be able to download.)  I just redownloaded it, and it has the same problem.
